#1-2

In answer to a distress call, Kerra returns to her Sith-controlled homeworld for a daring rescue . . . but her arrival on the planet coincides with an ambush from a Hutt mastermind! The clash with his invasion and a number of other unexpected surprises place Kerras small-scale rescue into a hot spot. She has to troubleshoot fast-and, as always, alone!
